title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Bodega Girls
description:
In "Oh Hello!," meet the four members of Bodega Girls, featuring special guest Anthony Rossomando, and Isom Innis of Foster the People who produced the band's new song at Converse Rubber Tracks. Hear how the band got their name and also the origins of the track, which Isom originally received a demo of in 2010. 
For more Converse Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
